{"id": 900, "genre": 1001, "title": "你有/你见过哪些龟毛的偶像包袱？", "description": "虽然不是却总是有网红的自知的一类朋友。（题图来自：HELENA PEREZ GARCIA）", "record_count": 2599, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607021837075RSWBLde8GyHsb2V.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-31T11:01:24Z", "options": [{"id": 62976, "content": "“今天没化妆，千万别拍我！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239090}, {"id": 62977, "content": "只是随意下班聚个餐而已，却见到她穿着妆容打扮的像名媛", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239090}, {"id": 62978, "content": "不想好明天穿什么今晚就不睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536887}, {"id": 62979, "content": "今天穿的衣服是去年的款 低头快速走过", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536887}, {"id": 62980, "content": "好烦辣，我们又不是台湾人，讲这些话都听不懂了辣！要怎样辣。????", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414097}, {"id": 62982, "content": "怎么感觉你们都在说我！?可是我现在才知道特么这些叫偶像包袱？我是冤枉的", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518454}, {"id": 62983, "content": "每天不发朋友圈就觉得今天没过过；每次朋友圈必须凑满九张照片；所有照片都虚化处理；所有人物照都秀秀磨皮——其实长得就又黑又一般还带绿茶婊属性", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 62984, "content": "聚餐精心打扮难道不是表现对对方的重视？不要自己邋遢随便就看不惯和自己不一样的素养", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493988}, {"id": 62986, "content": "看不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488918}, {"id": 62987, "content": "大家写的我全中?", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358319}, {"id": 62989, "content": "木有颜值只能靠才华，只重发有错别字的内容", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363108}, {"id": 64015, "content": "從來不發朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 371495}, {"id": 62998, "content": "Po图必有自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374869}, {"id": 62999, "content": "重要的事情说三遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414491}, {"id": 63000, "content": "毕业了就把我删了，过了两年我才发现。呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 63001, "content": "我是处女座～", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531274}, {"id": 63002, "content": "『我的世界没人懂』系列.让我尴尬症都犯了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541589}, {"id": 63003, "content": "『我的世界没人懂』系列.让我尴尬症都犯了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541589}, {"id": 63004, "content": "穿衣风格显而易见可不就偶像包袱嘛～ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541603}, {"id": 63008, "content": "ya", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541790}, {"id": 63010, "content": "龟毛是什么意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541984}, {"id": 63011, "content": "黄子韬删微博啊！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486495}, {"id": 63012, "content": "龟毛是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541992}, {"id": 63013, "content": "我只买最低配置。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 63014, "content": "高冷女神玩游戏，说话声音特小，一次两三个字。男子纷纷高潮护花。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540792}, {"id": 63022, "content": "我就静静地看你们龟毛", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161542zgUwEq1tAc4QIafh.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542048}, {"id": 62255, "content": "不愿意跟不熟的人打球，怕打得不好被笑话 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 62256, "content": "只参加自己擅长的社交活动 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 62257, "content": "我交朋友不在乎瘦不瘦，只要没我瘦就可以了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 62258, "content": "老删自己朋友圈，不好笑删，说太直白了删，这流行语都过时两个礼拜之久了删删删 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 233, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 63027, "content": "公开批斗我", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542059}, {"id": 63028, "content": "你们说的我都中了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345064}, {"id": 63030, "content": "每天洗头发算吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541143}, {"id": 64054, "content": "永远嫌自己胖 永远担心自己的减肥计划 问题是人根本不胖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 516629}, {"id": 63035, "content": "什么是龟毛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525157}, {"id": 63291, "content": "爽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 544505}, {"id": 63036, "content": "看了前几条，中了好几枪", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252687}, {"id": 63038, "content": "啊！给大家科普一下，龟毛就是一些麻烦，啰嗦的让人抓狂的行为，发音：孤摸。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542160}, {"id": 63040, "content": "莫名奇妙的口音，没有下限的智商。我只想问所谓偶像就不能正常么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59914}, {"id": 63041, "content": "什么叫龟毛？什么叫偶像包袱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142082}, {"id": 63042, "content": "习惯性否定别人，明明是好心想要分享，听完就说，切，这有什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535658}, {"id": 63043, "content": "一张自拍倒几个app修半小时?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540803}, {"id": 63299, "content": "发了删发了删发了删 卧槽你当时发干嘛啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 544538}, {"id": 63044, "content": "一张自拍倒5个app修半小时?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540803}, {"id": 63046, "content": "没洗头 不拍照", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540547}, {"id": 63047, "content": "罗辑思维", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 309490}, {"id": 63048, "content": "只要有人自拍随时都要入镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 534844}, {"id": 63049, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530141}, {"id": 63050, "content": "所以到底什么是龟毛…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 534558}, {"id": 63062, "content": "我是处女座，耶～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522295}]}